sentense =  subject + verb
            (பெயர் சொல்) + (வினை / செயல்)
  subject: 
i
you
we
they
he
she
it
names

  be verbs:
  two types:
  1) action verb (வேலை - play eat cook study)
  2) state verb (நிலை - be verb - be calm,be strong,he is a doctor,i am student)

 be verbs:
==========
1)   present form: am, are, is
      I - AM
      he,she,it - is
      they,you,we - are
ii)  post form: was , were
      I,he,she,it - was
      we,you,they - were
iii)  future form:
        all subjects --> will be
          ex: i will be happy
             you will be happy
              he will be happy
             he will be at school

